<item>
            <title>[HBASE-5952] Sync hardcoded default flush size and max file size with hbase-default.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5952</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since the hardcoded default flush size is 64MB, but the default in hbase-default.xml is 128MB, if the client does set it to 64MB,&lt;br/&gt;
the actual flush size will be 128MB instead, due to the way HRegion get the flush size. We can change how HRegion get the flush size,&lt;br/&gt;
but it is clean and simple to sync up the defaults.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
